### Delete Volunteer Account (requires authentication)
# First login to get token
@jwt_token = token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.volunteer@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### Delete Volunteer Account - Valid Request
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/volunteers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Delete Volunteer Account - Unauthorized (no token)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/volunteers/1

### Delete Volunteer Account - Invalid ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/volunteers/abc
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Delete Volunteer Account - Try to delete another user's account
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/volunteers/999
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
